  <summary date="2022-05-03T15:02:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Codifying Useful Regulatory Definitions Act or the CURD Act

This bill provides statutory authority for a definition of natural cheese. Under the bill, natural cheese is defined as cheese that is produced from animal milk or certain dairy ingredients and is produced in accordance with established cheese-making standards.</summary>
